meanings.definition: The twelfth in a series of twelve.
meanings.sent1: This is the dozenth cookie in the jar.
meanings.sent2: The dozenth month of the year is December.
meanings.sent3: I always lose count, but the dozenth cookie is my favorite.
meanings.sent4: The dozenth star in the sky shone the brightest.
meanings.sent5: The dozenth snowflake was the most intricate and beautiful.

meanings.sent1: She only ate a dozenth of the cake.
meanings.sent2: The dozenth of the puzzle pieces was missing.
meanings.sent3: I saved the dozenth piece for last because it's the tastiest.
meanings.sent4: The dozenth key unlocked the hidden treasure.
meanings.sent5: The dozenth petal on the flower was a different color than the rest.
